data.description: Nestled in a prime corner lot, this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom sanctuary with a 2-car garage is the epitome of modern living combined with outdoor leisure. This home offers a spacious, open floor plan perfect for gathering and entertaining! Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, tiled backsplash, and plenty of counter and storage space! Large primary suite with plenty of room for all your furniture! Spacious secondary bedrooms are a plus! Step out back to this Texas backyard with a covered patio and POOL ready for memories to be made with loved ones! Seller will pay buyers closing costs. All back backyard furniture conveys. Just a short drive to restaurants, refineries, great schools & only a few minutes to the beach! COME SEE IT TODAY!
